cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.HC, cs.IT, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the correlation between QoS and QoE for multimedia services, which involves both networking (cs.NI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) aspects. The focus on multimedia services suggests a likely category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses optimization techniques (cs.IT) and the subjective nature of QoE (cs.SI).
